config R8169SOC
	tristate "Realtek RTD129x SoC Gigabit Ethernet driver"
	depends on ARCH_RTD129X || COMPILE_TEST
	select PHYLIB
	help
	  This driver supports the integrated Gigabit Ethernet controller
	  found in Realtek RTD129x SoCs (RTD1294, RTD1295, RTD1296).

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here. The module
	  will be called r8169soc.
